Description:
[h1]CountryMo presents: Tic-Tac-Toe[/h1]
[hr][/hr]
1v1 game
Just a classic TicTacToe game  
Recommended settings: Unlimited boost, X goals to win, 1v1. 
You can also change the orange team name to X and the blue one to O
To reset the board just hit the red cube

Huge thanks to Mr. Swaggles, Mr. Phil, zach (first 2oops SSL), Martinn and Llamalectric | IT guy. 

Inspired by Leth's dart board map
